```plantuml
@startuml OAID_Tengine

package "Tengine Lite" {
    [Model Conversion Tools] as ModelConversion
    [Inference Engine] as InferenceEngine
    [Operator Library] as OperatorLibrary
    [Testing Framework] as TestingFramework

    package "Core Components" {
        [Device Abstraction Layer] as DeviceLayer
        [Graph Representation] as GraphIR
        [Operator Prototypes] as OperatorPrototypes
        [Memory Management] as MemoryMgmt
    }

    package "Hardware Backends" {
        [CPU Backend] as CPU
        [GPU Backend] as GPU
        [NPU Backend] as NPU
    }

    package "Utilities" {
        [Python Bindings] as PythonAPI
        [Image Processing] as ImageUtils
        [Online Reporting] as Reporting
    }
}

ModelConversion --> GraphIR : Generates\nTM2 format
InferenceEngine --> DeviceLayer : Uses
InferenceEngine --> GraphIR : Executes
InferenceEngine --> OperatorLibrary : Calls
OperatorLibrary --> OperatorPrototypes : Implements
OperatorLibrary --> MemoryMgmt : Uses
TestingFramework --> OperatorLibrary : Validates
TestingFramework --> InferenceEngine : Tests

DeviceLayer --> CPU : Manages
DeviceLayer --> GPU : Manages
DeviceLayer --> NPU : Manages

PythonAPI --> InferenceEngine : Wraps
ImageUtils --> InferenceEngine : Supports
Reporting --> InferenceEngine : Collects data

@enduml
```